text:
Dishonest, doesn’t pay for what’s due. I will never deal with her again. Be careful if you should choose to.

It has been 1 CNY and another is coming up, still haven’t pay.

If you want to deal with a dishonest owner, she’s the one to go to!

Rather throw my money away than deal with this parasite.
Auntie is very friendly and her goods & snacks are very reasonably priced 👍🏻 rare few shops at our local market, pls support before they disappear.
Friendly owner, fresh biscuits, reasonably priced!
